<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē śailaratnatriṇayanagaṇitē jyēṣṭada
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rśśōparāgē vikhyātē bhaumavārē tribhuvanapatayē bhīma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nāthāya bhaktyā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādāddoḍḍādibhūpārjjunavaravanitā kō
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭadakkāṁbikēya<unclear>ṁ</unclear> grāmaṁ maḍvāḍasaṁjñaṁ sakalakṛ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṣiyutaṁ vīranākhyātmajā <unclear>sā</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavatsara 1197 gu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>neṁṭi śrīma<unclear>ttri</unclear>bhuvanacakravartti śrīrājādhirājadēvara vi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ja<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied>rājyasaṁvatsaraṁbulu 59 gu śrāhi <unclear>śrē</unclear>ṣṭamāsamu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na Amāvāsya maṁgaḷavāramunāṁṭi sūryyagrahaṇa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>munāṁḍu dākṣārāma śrībhīmeśvaraśrīmahādēvaradavana
<lb n="10" break="no"/>punnamanāṁṭi ḍōlōtsavamunāṁṭi AvibaliArccana
<lb n="11" break="no"/>laku Oḍḍādi Arjjunadēvarāju dēvi koṁḍikamunnū<unclear>ṭi</unclear> A
<lb n="12" break="no"/><unclear>ḍapa</unclear> gaḍiyapaseṭṭi vīrapanēni kūṁtuṟu Akkāsānki nō
<lb n="13" break="no"/>mugā Arjjunadēvaṁḍu dhārāpūrvva<unclear>kamu</unclear>cēsi Āca
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṁdrārkkamugaṁ beṭṭina maḍuvāḍa<unclear>nu</unclear> yūru Okkaṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

